 ISP to use the WI solution  or use a VMI mobile PC that has been configured to use the VMI EarthLink account s  Once connected via WI  users may access the following network resources depending on user access level  Network drives   Such as Departmental O  drive  Personal Directory M  drive  and the Public Directory P  drive  VMI email   via the Outlook client including accessing PST files on network drives Datatel Colleague  Without the need to install the client software on your remote computer  Remote Desktop   Access your VMI desktop computer from off Post Preston Library research databases It is suggested that all departments with mobile computers  and individuals who travel frequently  use the WI solution to ensure data integrity  Please follow the installation instructions to use WI  Web Interface Remote Access Instructions  Go to Web Interface  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 